  Source:
    Title: Harijan
    Editor: Mohandas Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 16 February 1934
---
He and His Law are one. The Law is God. Anything attributed to Him is not
a mere attribute. He is the attribute. He is Truth, Love and Law and a
million other things that human ingenuity can name.
